      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered in a garage its whole life and has been kept meticulously clean\u2014you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust. It drives like a dream and is ready for someone who truly appreciates a car that's been loved this much. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself!",
