    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is an analog masterpiece featuring the M97.01 3.8L flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed G97 manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) for adaptive damping, ensuring surgical turn-in and mid-corner stability. Mechanically pristine, the vehicle has undergone a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a full bore-scope inspection to confirm cylinder wall integrity. The naturally aspirated induction note is enhanced by a factory Sport Exhaust (PSE). With zero deferred maintenance and a documented service history, this is a turn-key example for the discerning driver.",
